105
00:08:08.633 --> 00:08:10.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I unsealed Morn's will.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:08:12.212 --> 00:08:13.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He left everything to you.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:08:14.512 --> 00:08:17.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me? He left everything to me?</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:08:18.431 --> 00:08:19.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:08:21.870 --> 00:08:23.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn...</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:08:25.068 --> 00:08:27.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>dear, sweet Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:08:28.507 --> 00:08:29.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:41.584 --> 00:08:45.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The poor fool actually believed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you cared about him.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:45.263 --> 00:08:46.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:46.343 --> 00:08:48.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was up for hours</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>last night thinking about him.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:48.362 --> 00:08:50.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Calculating his net worth, no doubt.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:08:50.841 --> 00:08:52.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We spent a lot of time together, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:08:52.781 --> 00:08:54.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were obviously a lot closer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than I ever realized.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:08:56.739 --> 00:08:58.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>His financial records.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:09:02.238 --> 00:09:03.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is this some kind of joke?</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:09:03.678 --> 00:09:04.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you mean?</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:09:04.738 --> 00:09:05.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to this, he was broke.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:09:06.258 --> 00:09:07.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sarcastically ) No.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:09:08.016 --> 00:09:08.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How can that be?</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:09:10.334 --> 00:09:11.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He paid his bar bill</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the end of every month.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:09:11.555 --> 00:09:13.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That kind of money</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>must have come from somewhere.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:09:13.914 --> 00:09:16.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, he did have his shipping business.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:09:17.053 --> 00:09:20.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe all his assets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are tied up in inventory.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:09:21.132 --> 00:09:23.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course. Inventory.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:09:26.610 --> 00:09:30.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll unload everything,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and use the profits to...</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:09:31.209 --> 00:09:33.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, what's that smell?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Your inheritance.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:09:34.129 --> 00:09:36.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Livanian beets. Very ripe.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:09:37.547 --> 00:09:38.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's in the rest of these?</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:09:39.307 --> 00:09:40.088 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>More beets.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:09:41.206 --> 00:09:44.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it? That's all he had?</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:09:44.386 --> 00:09:45.067 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm afraid so.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:09:45.265 --> 00:09:46.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:09:48.324 --> 00:09:52.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Except for the contents of his quarters.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe he spent all his money</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:09:52.923 --> 00:09:57.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-on furnishings and works of art.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Objets d'art.</i></c.bg_transparent>

139
00:09:57.401 --> 00:09:58.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:09:59.521 --> 00:10:01.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Objets d'art.</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:10:02.360 --> 00:10:04.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll hold an auction.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>People will pay a premium</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:10:04.659 --> 00:10:06.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to own something that used to be Morn's.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:10:12.137 --> 00:10:13.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you sure these are the right quarters?</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:10:14.097 --> 00:10:15.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:10:15.816 --> 00:10:16.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Figures.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:10:18.615 --> 00:10:19.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:10:20.174 --> 00:10:22.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That, I believe, is a matador.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:10:23.611 --> 00:10:25.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. That.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:10:25.813 --> 00:10:27.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: That's Morn's bed.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:10:27.932 --> 00:10:28.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn slept in...</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:10:29.892 --> 00:10:31.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>-mud? -Hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:10:32.031 --> 00:10:33.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm told it's excellent for the skin.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:10:38.429 --> 00:10:39.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks, Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:10:39.929 --> 00:10:41.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just what I always wanted.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:10:42.207 --> 00:10:43.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping )</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:10:46.486 --> 00:10:48.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing in my mud?</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:10:48.826 --> 00:10:53.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I... I couldn't resist.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Morny and I had so many happy times here,</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:10:53.649 --> 00:10:58.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just... I had to slip in.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry if I startled you.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:10:58.765 --> 00:11:01.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I heard you coming in</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I thought I'd better hide.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:11:01.902 --> 00:11:02.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who are you?</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:11:03.508 --> 00:11:04.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um...</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:11:04.581 --> 00:11:05.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Larell.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:11:06.340 --> 00:11:08.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn's wife. Well, ex-wife.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:11:08.980 --> 00:11:09.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn was married?</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:11:10.720 --> 00:11:11.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To you?</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:11:11.678 --> 00:11:13.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For two wonderful years.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:11:14.278 --> 00:11:16.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must be Quark.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:11:17.141 --> 00:11:19.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morny and I kept in touch</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after we were separated.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:11:20.216 --> 00:11:22.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He talked about you all the time.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:11:24.895 --> 00:11:25.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's nice.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:11:26.194 --> 00:11:28.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He told me that if anything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ever happened to him,</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:11:29.074 --> 00:11:31.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>he wanted you to have everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that was ever his.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:11:33.513 --> 00:11:34.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Everything?</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:11:36.351 --> 00:11:37.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Everything.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:11:40.310 --> 00:11:41.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm glad you came by,</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:11:42.993 --> 00:11:46.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because Morny didn't leave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>me much of anything else.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:11:46.969 --> 00:11:48.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why, I find that hard to believe.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:11:48.688 --> 00:11:49.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughs )</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:11:50.427 --> 00:11:52.328 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm as disappointed as you are.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:11:53.326 --> 00:11:54.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I happen to know</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:11:54.027 --> 00:11:57.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that he had quite</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a substantial retirement fund,</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:11:57.746 --> 00:12:00.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>one that could make two people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>very comfortable.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:12:02.644 --> 00:12:06.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you're partial to mud,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's comfortable, all right.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:12:07.242 --> 00:12:10.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm talking about the thousand bricks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of gold-pressed latinum</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:12:10.122 --> 00:12:12.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that he won in the Lissepian Lottery.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:12:12.441 --> 00:12:14.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A thousand bricks?</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:12:14.440 --> 00:12:18.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mm-hmm. Now that he's gone, it's all ours.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:12:30.475 --> 00:12:33.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( vacuum slurping )</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:12:45.271 --> 00:12:46.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:12:47.583 --> 00:12:49.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you think?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm looking for the latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:12:50.389 --> 00:12:52.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must know where he kept it.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:12:54.469 --> 00:12:57.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't even know it existed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>until you told me.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:13:01.446 --> 00:13:03.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm sure it's somewhere</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the station.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:13:05.259 --> 00:13:06.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do we know he didn't spend it already?</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:13:06.766 --> 00:13:08.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you, it was for his retirement.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:13:09.451 --> 00:13:12.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Poor Morn.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He never got a chance to enjoy it.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:13:13.802 --> 00:13:15.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But that doesn't mean we can't.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:13:16.842 --> 00:13:18.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know what you're doing.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:13:19.842 --> 00:13:20.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What am I doing?</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:13:21.541 --> 00:13:22.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just so we're clear...</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:13:23.600 --> 00:13:25.582 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the latinum's mine.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:13:27.019 --> 00:13:31.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He may have left everything to you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I was his wife.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:13:31.618 --> 00:13:35.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could contest the will,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and tie you up in court for years.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:13:35.996 --> 00:13:36.596 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:13:37.656 --> 00:13:40.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But there's no reason</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it has to come to that.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:13:40.415 --> 00:13:43.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After all, a thousand bricks is plenty</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for both of us.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:13:44.193 --> 00:13:45.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is a lot of money.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:13:48.292 --> 00:13:53.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And as soon as we find it,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we'll take a nice long vacation together.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:13:54.690 --> 00:13:57.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn would have wanted it that way.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:13:57.510 --> 00:13:59.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course, he would have.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:14:07.707 --> 00:14:11.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The latinum's not on the station.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I looked everywhere. Evade.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:14:11.766 --> 00:14:14.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I even had my brother scan for it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the internal sensors.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:14:14.765 --> 00:14:16.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, at least you have the painting.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:14:16.205 --> 00:14:18.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, forget the painting.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I want that latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:14:19.403 --> 00:14:20.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you think it'll make you happy.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:14:20.844 --> 00:14:21.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Confront.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:14:21.742 --> 00:14:23.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Believe me, it will.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:14:25.405 --> 00:14:27.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is the break I've been waiting for,</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:14:27.921 --> 00:14:29.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and it's been a long time in coming.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:14:30.441 --> 00:14:33.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want Morn's money. I need Morn's money.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:14:33.142 --> 00:14:33.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I deserve Morn's money.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:14:37.177 --> 00:14:37.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your move.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:14:40.437 --> 00:14:44.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Beautiful, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>
