233
00:15:09.748 --> 00:15:10.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What could I do?</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:15:11.329 --> 00:15:11.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Retreat.</c.bg_transparent>

235
