240
00:15:30.082 --> 00:15:31.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not me.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:15:32.022 --> 00:15:34.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course not. Acquire.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:15:49.296 --> 00:15:50.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
