264
00:16:57.515 --> 00:16:58.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:17:00.076 --> 00:17:03.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
