269
00:17:16.436 --> 00:17:16.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We trusted Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:17:18.346 --> 00:17:24.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
