303
00:18:50.083 --> 00:18:50.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me, too.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:18:51.323 --> 00:18:52.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
