306
00:18:59.365 --> 00:18:59.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't try anything.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:19:00.312 --> 00:19:02.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
