314
00:19:42.586 --> 00:19:45.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn, wherever you are, I love you!</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:19:49.527 --> 00:19:51.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you mean</c.bg_transparent>
