322
00:20:12.038 --> 00:20:13.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That can't be it.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:20:14.038 --> 00:20:16.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Storage Locker 137.</c.bg_transparent>

324
