<c.bg_transparent>someone broke into the Central Bank</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and made off with...</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:32:00.715 --> 00:32:03.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>One thousand bricks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of gold-pressed latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:32:07.513 --> 00:32:08.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wait a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:32:09.174 --> 00:32:12.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You expect me to believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that the four of you pulled that off?</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:32:12.758 --> 00:32:14.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was five of us. Morn helped.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:32:15.100 --> 00:32:17.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, but then he ran off with the latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:32:18.499 --> 00:32:19.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why did you take</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so long to come after him?</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:32:20.079 --> 00:32:22.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because we knew he'd stashed it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>away somewhere</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:32:22.442 --> 00:32:24.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to wait for the statute</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of limitations to expire.</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:32:24.801 --> 00:32:26.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And it did, two weeks ago.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:32:26.521 --> 00:32:28.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see, we can't be prosecuted anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:32:29.360 --> 00:32:30.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So here we are.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:32:30.680 --> 00:32:31.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The latinum's en route.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:32:33.422 --> 00:32:37.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we should just split it up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and go our separate ways.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:32:37.866 --> 00:32:38.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The voice of reason.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:32:39.208 --> 00:32:39.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not you...</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:32:42.967 --> 00:32:43.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>us.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:32:44.207 --> 00:32:45.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Krit's right. We don't need him anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:32:58.748 --> 00:32:59.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So what do we do with him?</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:32:59.968 --> 00:33:01.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KRIT: It should look like an accident.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:33:02.246 --> 00:33:04.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We don't want anyone asking questions.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:33:05.820 --> 00:33:07.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wait a minute. You can't kill me.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:33:07.925 --> 00:33:09.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm the only one who can take</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>delivery of the latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:33:09.865 --> 00:33:10.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You need my thumb print.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:33:11.788 --> 00:33:13.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you stand still,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this won't hurt as much.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:33:14.147 --> 00:33:14.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screaming )</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:33:15.147 --> 00:33:16.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>HAIN: Ah, ah, ah, wait a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:33:17.328 --> 00:33:18.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you propose, Nahsk?</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:33:19.128 --> 00:33:21.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That we walk into the Cargo Bay</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with his bloody thumb,</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:33:21.570 --> 00:33:22.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and ask for the latinum?</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:33:23.464 --> 00:33:24.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We need him.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:33:33.982 --> 00:33:37.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only question is,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what happens after he takes delivery?</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:33:41.280 --> 00:33:44.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We could split the latinum... five ways.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:33:44.983 --> 00:33:47.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That is what you would</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have gotten if Morn was still alive.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:33:47.662 --> 00:33:49.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's true.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:33:50.038 --> 00:33:51.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Think of me as Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:33:51.749 --> 00:33:52.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't believe I just said that.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:33:53.385 --> 00:33:55.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This isn't fair. We stole it.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:33:55.206 --> 00:33:56.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He had nothing to do with it.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:33:56.468 --> 00:33:58.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe not, but the bottom line</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is you need me.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:34:00.376 --> 00:34:02.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A thousand bricks of latinum</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>split five ways...</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:34:06.534 --> 00:34:07.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>what do you think?</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:34:09.173 --> 00:34:10.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's still a lot of latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:34:11.452 --> 00:34:14.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's 250 bricks each.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:34:16.514 --> 00:34:17.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So do we have a deal?</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:34:22.153 --> 00:34:23.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-All right.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-OK.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:34:23.832 --> 00:34:26.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Bolian transport</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>arrives tomorrow at 1600.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:34:27.511 --> 00:34:28.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll meet at the cargo bay.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:34:28.711 --> 00:34:30.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're staying together until it gets here.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:34:31.287 --> 00:34:31.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are?</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:34:31.491 --> 00:34:33.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't trust you, and I certainly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>don't trust them.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:34:34.471 --> 00:34:35.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see your point.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:34:36.013 --> 00:34:38.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I have a bar to run.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:34:42.371 --> 00:34:43.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:34:48.409 --> 00:34:49.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To your hospitality.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:34:50.091 --> 00:34:50.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't mention it.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:34:55.569 --> 00:34:56.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So this was Morn's favorite place?</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:34:57.955 --> 00:34:59.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He used to sit right there.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:34:59.208 --> 00:35:03.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, that's not very smart</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sitting with your back to the door.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:35:04.272 --> 00:35:06.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was the trusting type.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:35:07.391 --> 00:35:08.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Which one of you killed him anyway?</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:35:10.390 --> 00:35:11.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wasn't us.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:35:14.614 --> 00:35:15.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me neither.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:35:16.468 --> 00:35:17.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't look at me.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:35:18.390 --> 00:35:19.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then it really was an accident.</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:35:21.715 --> 00:35:24.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Poor Morny. He always had such bad luck.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:35:30.953 --> 00:35:31.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get rid of him.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:35:35.351 --> 00:35:36.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're closed.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:35:37.271 --> 00:35:38.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>At this hour?</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:35:40.522 --> 00:35:41.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Friends of Morn.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:35:42.197 --> 00:35:43.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're... commiserating.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:35:44.636 --> 00:35:46.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:35:47.861 --> 00:35:49.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And how long are you going to be closed?</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:35:50.421 --> 00:35:54.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, until about 1600 hours tomorrow.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:35:56.204 --> 00:35:57.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have a lot to commiserate about.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:35:58.603 --> 00:35:59.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:36:08.318 --> 00:36:08.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where were we?</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:36:17.198 --> 00:36:18.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There it is.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:36:18.797 --> 00:36:19.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Right on time.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:36:21.956 --> 00:36:22.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh...</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:36:23.156 --> 00:36:25.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I believe that's for me.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:36:41.150 --> 00:36:42.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Open it.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:36:53.907 --> 00:36:55.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:36:56.146 --> 00:36:57.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll count it.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:36:58.385 --> 00:36:59.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:37:09.222 --> 00:37:10.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:37:11.043 --> 00:37:12.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Somebody else count it.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:37:12.905 --> 00:37:17.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Put it down, Hain. My brother may be slow,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but if you pull that trigger,</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:37:18.970 --> 00:37:19.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>he'll kill you.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:37:21.609 --> 00:37:23.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not slow.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:37:29.047 --> 00:37:30.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nahsk...</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:37:31.469 --> 00:37:32.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>what are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:37:34.154 --> 00:37:35.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're family.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:37:35.376 --> 00:37:37.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just put the gun down.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:37:48.491 --> 00:37:50.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( weapons fire continues )</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:37:52.210 --> 00:37:53.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:37:54.049 --> 00:37:55.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kill each other.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:37:57.009 --> 00:37:57.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:38:01.047 --> 00:38:03.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:38:03.167 --> 00:38:05.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: Security. Drop your weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:38:05.406 --> 00:38:07.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Huh?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( weapons fire continues )</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:38:07.488 --> 00:38:10.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: This is your last warning.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I said drop them.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:38:10.288 --> 00:38:11.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( weapon clatters to ground )</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:38:11.270 --> 00:38:11.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>LARELL: I surrender.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:38:14.310 --> 00:38:15.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take her to a holding cell.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:38:15.989 --> 00:38:17.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get the rest of them to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:38:25.146 --> 00:38:27.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, there you are.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:38:27.586 --> 00:38:28.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are they gone?</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:38:29.446 --> 00:38:32.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>From now on,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll be commiserating alone.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:38:32.710 --> 00:38:34.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All your "friends" are going to prison.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:38:36.256 --> 00:38:36.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For how long?</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:38:37.295 --> 00:38:39.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Assault with intent to kill?</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:38:39.657 --> 00:38:40.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Long enough.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:38:41.399 --> 00:38:42.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then it's mine.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:38:43.318 --> 00:38:44.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All mine.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:38:46.701 --> 00:38:48.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What you are about to hear</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:38:49.003 --> 00:38:52.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>is the most beautiful sound in the galaxy.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:38:57.641 --> 00:38:59.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, that can't be.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:38:59.640 --> 00:39:01.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no latinum in these bricks.</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:39:01.640 --> 00:39:02.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:39:03.079 --> 00:39:06.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Someone's extracted all the latinum!</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:39:06.835 --> 00:39:08.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's nothing here but worthless gold.</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:39:09.158 --> 00:39:11.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And it's all yours.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:39:11.397 --> 00:39:12.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:39:13.935 --> 00:39:15.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:39:15.916 --> 00:39:19.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No! No!</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:39:34.391 --> 00:39:35.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:39:36.266 --> 00:39:38.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quark? Quark?</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:39:38.230 --> 00:39:39.029 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:39:39.949 --> 00:39:41.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you want?</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:39:41.188 --> 00:39:42.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's someone here to see you.</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:39:43.281 --> 00:39:45.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought you said</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they were all going to prison.</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:39:46.264 --> 00:39:47.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'd better sit down.</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:39:51.303 --> 00:39:52.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Morn?</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:39:52.302 --> 00:39:53.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Alive and well.</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:39:54.565 --> 00:39:56.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Apparently, he faked his own death,</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:39:57.411 --> 00:39:59.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I'll let him tell you all about it.</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:40:06.307 --> 00:40:07.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well?</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:40:07.666 --> 00:40:08.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:40:08.809 --> 00:40:09.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to hear it.</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:40:10.471 --> 00:40:11.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not one word.</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:40:12.553 --> 00:40:13.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You set me up.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:40:17.701 --> 00:40:19.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You left the latinum to me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>because you knew I would do</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:40:19.963 --> 00:40:21.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>whatever it would take</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get my hands on it.</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:40:22.336 --> 00:40:23.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You figured I could keep the four of them</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:40:24.038 --> 00:40:26.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>off-balance long enough for them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to turn on themselves.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:40:26.637 --> 00:40:30.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This whole thing was a scam</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get them off your back, wasn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:40:34.795 --> 00:40:36.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could have been killed, you know.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:40:43.592 --> 00:40:45.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I thought we were friends.</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:40:51.110 --> 00:40:52.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to admit...</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:40:52.750 --> 00:40:55.092 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't suspect for a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:40:55.433 --> 00:40:56.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell you the truth,</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:40:56.655 --> 00:40:58.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't think you had it in you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to pull off something like this.</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:40:59.654 --> 00:41:01.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just have one question for you.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:41:01.214 --> 00:41:02.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened to the latinum?</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:41:14.010 --> 00:41:17.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gurgling burp )</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:41:22.327 --> 00:41:25.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course. Your second stomach.</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:41:28.419 --> 00:41:30.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've been keeping it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in your second stomach</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:41:30.245 --> 00:41:31.805 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>all these years?</c.bg_transparent>

707
00:41:33.764 --> 00:41:35.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's a lot of latinum.</c.bg_transparent>

708
00:41:35.083 --> 00:41:36.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No wonder your hair fell out.</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:41:43.241 --> 00:41:44.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For me?</c.bg_transparent>

710
00:41:48.760 --> 00:41:54.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That must be 100 bricks worth.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what to say.</c.bg_transparent>

711
00:41:55.318 --> 00:41:56.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks.</c.bg_transparent>

712
00:41:56.338 --> 00:41:58.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not that I didn't earn it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after all you put me through.</c.bg_transparent>

713
00:42:01.377 --> 00:42:04.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you ever want to set</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>me up again, feel free.</c.bg_transparent>

714
00:42:07.622 --> 00:42:08.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know...</c.bg_transparent>

715
00:42:10.304 --> 00:42:12.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you and I should consider</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>doing business together.</c.bg_transparent>

716
00:42:13.447 --> 00:42:15.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Two enterprising gentlemen like us</c.bg_transparent>

717
00:42:16.110 --> 00:42:20.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>could do all right for ourselves.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Take that gold dust of yours...</c.bg_transparent>

718
00:42:22.589 --> 00:42:24.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it doesn't have to be a total loss.</c.bg_transparent>

719
00:42:25.411 --> 00:42:26.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hear there's some primitive cultures</c.bg_transparent>

720
00:42:26.971 --> 00:42:27.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>who consider it quite valuable.</c.bg_transparent>

